Program: Omnibus
Title: Adventures of the Spider Man
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376mhj
Last Broadcast Date: 15 October 2002
After introducing the collection of 200 tarantulas that he keeps in his spare bedroom, Martin Nicolas then takes off to the Tambopata Reserve in the Amazon Basin in search of a spider which has a body length of 95mm and a leg-span of 250mm. Picture: Tarantula, Credit: Getty Images